post_text:
We know that there is a lot of interest in tonight's Board Meeting. We just want to remind everyone that under the State of Illinois Guidelines in Phase 4 no more than 50 people can occupy a space. That being said space may be limited. The district would like to remind everyone that they may submit comments to the Board President Joe Haverly at jhaverly@nbcusd.org by 6:15 pm and the meeting is streamed https://trst.in/SHHd5L
We appreciate everyone's interest and are trying to offer other ways for people to be heard and stay informed under the current guidelines.
